#. module: sale
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/sale/static/src/js/tours/sale.js:0
msgid "<b>Congratulations</b>, your first quotation is sent!<br>Check your email to validate the quote."
msgstr ""
"<b>ຂໍສະແດງຄວາມຍິນດີ</b>, ໃບສະເໜີລາຄາທຳອິດຂອງທ່ານໄດ້ຖືກສົ່ງອອກແລ້ວ!<br>ກວດເບິ່ງອີເມວຂອງທ່ານເພື່"
"ອຢືນຢັນ."

#. module: sale
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/sale/static/src/js/tours/sale.js:0
