msgstr "ໂທເຄັນເຂົ້າເຖິງບໍ່ຖືກຕ້ອງ."

#. module: sale
#: model:ir.model.fields,help:sale.field_sale_advance_payment_inv__amount_to_invoice
msgid "The amount to invoice = Sale Order Total - Confirmed Down Payments."
msgstr "ຈຳນວນທີ່ຈະອອກໃບເກັບເງິນ = ຍອດລວມໃບສັ່ງຂາຍ - ເງິນມັດຈຳທີ່ຢືນຢັນແລ້ວ."

#. module: sale
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/sale/models/sale_order.py:0
msgid "The delivery date is sooner than the expected date. You may be unable to honor the delivery date."
msgstr ""
"ວັນທີສົ່ງສິນຄ້າແມ່ນໄວກວ່າວັນທີທີ່ຄາດໄວ້. ທ່ານອາດຈະບໍ່ສາມາດສົ່ງສິນຄ້າໄດ້ຕາມກຳນົດ."

#. module: sale
#: model:ir.model.fields,help:sale.field_sale_advance_payment_inv__fixed_amount
msgid "The fixed amount to be invoiced in advance."
msgstr "ຈຳນວນເງິນຄົງທີ່ທີ່ຈະອອກໃບເກັບເງິນລ່ວງໜ້າ."

#. module: sale
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/sale/models/product_template.py:0
msgid ""
"The following products cannot be restricted to the company %s because they have already been used in quotations or sales orders in another company:\n"
"%s\n"
"You can archive these products and recreate them with your company restriction instead, or leave them as shared product."
msgstr ""
"ຜະລິດຕະພັນຕໍ່ໄປນີ້ບໍ່ສາມາດຈຳກັດໃຫ້ໃຊ້ສະເພາະບໍລິສັດ %s ໄດ້ ເນື່ອງຈາກພວກມັນຖືກນຳໃຊ້ເຂົ້າໃນໃບສະເໜີລາຄາ "
"ຫຼື ໃບສັ່ງຂາຍໃນບໍລິສັດອື່ນແລ້ວ:\n"
"%s\n"
"ທ່ານສາມາດຈັດເກັບຜະລິດຕະພັນເຫຼົ່ານີ້ ແລະ ສ້າງພວກມັນຂຶ້ນໃໝ່ໂດຍກຳນົດໃຫ້ສະເພາະບໍລິສັດຂອງທ່ານແທນ, ຫຼື ປ່ອຍ"
"ໃຫ້ພວກມັນເປັນຜະລິດຕະພັນທີ່ໃຊ້ຮ່ວມກັນ."

#. module: sale
#: model:ir.model.fields,help:sale.field_res_config_settings__automatic_invoice
msgid ""
"The invoice is generated automatically and available in the customer portal when the transaction is confirmed by the payment provider.\n"
"The invoice is marked as paid and the payment is registered in the payment journal defined in the configuration of the payment provider.\n"
"This mode is advised if you issue the final invoice at the order and not after the delivery."
msgstr ""
"ໃບເກັບເງິນຈະຖືກສ້າງຂຶ້ນໂດຍອັດຕະໂນມັດ ແລະ ສາມາດເບິ່ງໄດ້ໃນພອດທໍລູກຄ້າເມື່ອທຸລະກຳຖືກຢືນຢັນໂດຍຜູ້ໃຫ້ບໍລິກາ"
"ນຊຳລະເງິນ."

#. module: sale
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:sale.res_config_settings_view_form
msgid "The margin is computed as the sum of product sales prices minus the cost set in their detail form."
msgstr ""
"ອັດຕາກຳໄລຖືກຄິດໄລ່ຈາກຜົນລວມຂອງລາຄາຂາຍສິນຄ້າ ລົບດ້ວຍຕົ້ນທຶນທີ່ຕັ້ງໄວ້ໃນຟອມລາຍລະອຽດ."

#. module: sale
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:sale.view_sale_advance_payment_inv
msgid "The new invoice will deduct draft invoices linked to this sale order."
msgstr "ໃບເກັບເງິນໃໝ່ຈະຫັກໃບເກັບເງິນສະບັບຮ່າງທີ່ເຊື່ອມໂຍງກັບໃບສັ່ງຂາຍນີ້."

#. module: sale
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:sale.sale_order_portal_template
msgid "The order is not in a state requiring customer payment."
msgstr "ໃບສັ່ງຊື້ບໍ່ໄດ້ຢູ່ໃນສະຖານະທີ່ຕ້ອງການການຊຳລະເງິນຈາກລູກຄ້າ."

#. module: sale
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/sale/controllers/portal.py:0
msgid "The order is not in a state requiring customer signature."
msgstr "ໃບສັ່ງຊື້ບໍ່ໄດ້ຢູ່ໃນສະຖານະທີ່ຕ້ອງການລາຍເຊັນຈາກລູກຄ້າ."

#. module: sale
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/sale/models/sale_order_line.py:0
msgid "The ordered quantity has been updated."
msgstr "ຈຳນວນທີ່ສັ່ງຊື້ໄດ້ຖືກອັບເດດແລ້ວ."

#. module: sale
#: model:ir.model.fields,help:sale.field_sale_order__reference
msgid "The payment communication of this sale order."
msgstr "ຂໍ້ມູນການຕິດຕໍ່ສື່ສານການຊຳລະເງິນຂອງໃບສັ່ງຂາຍນີ້."

#. module: sale
#: model:ir.model.fields,help:sale.field_sale_advance_payment_inv__amount
msgid "The percentage of amount to be invoiced in advance."
msgstr "ເປີເຊັນຂອງຈຳນວນເງິນທີ່ຈະອອກໃບເກັບເງິນລ່ວງໜ້າ."

#. module: sale
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/sale/wizard/sale_make_invoice_advance.py:0
msgid "The product used to invoice a down payment should be of type 'Service'. Please use another product or update this product."
msgstr ""
"ສິນຄ້າທີ່ໃຊ້ເພື່ອອອກໃບເກັບເງິນມັດຈຳຄວນເປັນປະເພດ 'ການບໍລິການ'. ກະລຸນາໃຊ້ສິນຄ້າອື່ນ ຫຼື ອັບເດດສິນຄ້ານີ້."

#. module: sale
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/sale/wizard/sale_make_invoice_advance.py:0
msgid "The product used to invoice a down payment should have an invoice policyset to \"Ordered quantities\". Please update your deposit product to be able to create a deposit invoice."
msgstr ""
"ສິນຄ້າທີ່ໃຊ້ເພື່ອອອກໃບເກັບເງິນມັດຈຳຄວນມີນະໂຍບາຍການອອກໃບເກັບເງິນເປັນ \"ຈຳນວນທີ່ສັ່ງຊື້\"."

#. module: sale
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/sale/controllers/portal.py:0
msgid "The provided parameters are invalid."
msgstr "ພາລາມິເຕີທີ່ໃຫ້ມາບໍ່ຖືກຕ້ອງ."

#. module: sale
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/sale/wizard/sale_make_invoice_advance.py:0
msgid "The value of the down payment amount must be positive."
msgstr "ມູນຄ່າຂອງຈຳນວນເງິນມັດຈຳຕ້ອງເປັນຄ່າບວກ."

#. module: sale
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:sale.portal_my_orders
msgid "There are currently no orders for your account."
msgstr "ປະຈຸບັນບໍ່ມີໃບສັ່ງຊື້ສຳລັບບັນຊີຂອງທ່ານ."

#. module: sale
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:sale.portal_my_quotations
msgid "There are currently no quotations for your account."
msgstr "ປະຈຸບັນບໍ່ມີໃບສະເໜີລາຄາສຳລັບບັນຊີຂອງທ່ານ."

#. module: sale
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:sale.view_sale_advance_payment_inv
msgid "There are existing"
msgstr "ມີຢູ່ແລ້ວ"

#. module: sale
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/sale/models/sale_order.py:0
msgid ""
"There is nothing to invoice!\n"
"\n"
"Reason(s) of this behavior could be:\n"
"- You should deliver your products before invoicing them.\n"
"- You should modify the invoicing policy of your product: Open the product, go to the \"Sales\" tab and modify invoicing policy from \"delivered quantities\" to \"ordered quantities\". For Services, you should modify the Service Invoicing Policy to 'Prepaid'."
msgstr ""
"ບໍ່ມີລາຍການທີ່ຈະອອກໃບເກັບເງິນ!\n"
"\n"
"ເຫດຜົນອາດຈະເປັນ:\n"
"- ທ່ານຄວນສົ່ງສິນຄ້າກ່ອນທີ່ຈະອອກໃບເກັບເງິນ.\n"
"- ທ່ານຄວນແກ້ໄຂນະໂຍບາຍການອອກໃບເກັບເງິນຂອງສິນຄ້າ: ເປີດສິນຄ້າ, ໄປທີ່ແຖບ \"ການຂາຍ\" ແລະ ປ່ຽນນ"
"ະໂຍບາຍຈາກ \"ຈຳນວນທີ່ສົ່ງແລ້ວ\" ເປັນ \"ຈຳນວນທີ່ສັ່ງຊື້\"."

#. module: sale
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:sale.res_config_settings_view_form
msgid "This default value is applied to any new product created. This can be changed in the product detail form."
msgstr ""
"ຄ່າເລີ່ມຕົ້ນນີ້ຈະຖືກນຳໃຊ້ກັບສິນຄ້າໃໝ່ທຸກລາຍການທີ່ສ້າງຂຶ້ນ. ສາມາດປ່ຽນແປງໄດ້ໃນຟອມລາຍລະອຽດສິນຄ້າ."

#. module: sale
#: model:ir.model.fields,help:sale.field_account_bank_statement_line__campaign_id
#: model:ir.model.fields,help:sale.field_account_move__campaign_id
#: model:ir.model.fields,help:sale.field_account_payment__campaign_id
#: model:ir.model.fields,help:sale.field_sale_order__campaign_id
msgid "This is a name that helps you keep track of your different campaign efforts, e.g. Fall_Drive, Christmas_Special"
msgstr ""
"ນີ້ແມ່ນຊື່ທີ່ຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ທ່ານຕິດຕາມຄວາມພະຍາຍາມໃນແຄມເປນຕ່າງໆຂອງທ່ານ, ເຊັ່ນ: Fall_Drive, "
"Christmas_Special"

#. module: sale
#: model:ir.model.fields,help:sale.field_sale_order__commitment_date
msgid "This is the delivery date promised to the customer. If set, the delivery order will be scheduled based on this date rather than product lead times."
msgstr ""
"ນີ້ແມ່ນວັນທີສົ່ງສິນຄ້າທີ່ສັນຍາກັບລູກຄ້າ. ຖ້າຕັ້ງໄວ້, ໃບສົ່ງສິນຄ້າຈະຖືກກຳນົດເວລາຕາມວັນທີນີ້ແທນທີ່ຈະເປັນໄລຍະເວລ"
"ານຳສົ່ງສິນຄ້າ."

#. module: sale
#: model:ir.model.fields,help:sale.field_account_bank_statement_line__medium_id
#: model:ir.model.fields,help:sale.field_account_move__medium_id
#: model:ir.model.fields,help:sale.field_account_payment__medium_id
#: model:ir.model.fields,help:sale.field_sale_order__medium_id
