msgstr "ໃບສັ່ງຊື້ຂອງທ່ານໄດ້ຖືກເຊັນແລ້ວ."

#. module: sale
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:sale.sale_order_portal_template
msgid "Your order is not in a state to be rejected."
msgstr "ໃບສັ່ງຊື້ຂອງທ່ານບໍ່ໄດ້ຢູ່ໃນສະຖານະທີ່ຈະຖືກປະຕິເສດໄດ້."

#. module: sale
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/sale/models/sale_order.py:0
msgid ""
"Your quotation contains products from company %(product_company)s whereas your quotation belongs to company %(quote_company)s. \n"
" Please change the company of your quotation or remove the products from other companies (%(bad_products)s)."
msgstr ""
"ໃບສະເໜີລາຄາຂອງທ່ານມີສິນຄ້າຈາກບໍລິສັດ %(product_company)s ໃນຂະນະທີ່ໃບສະເໜີລາຄາຂອງທ່ານເປັນຂອ"
"ງບໍລິສັດ %(quote_company)s. \n"
" ກະລຸນາປ່ຽນບໍລິສັດຂອງໃບສະເໜີລາຄາ ຫຼື ລຶບສິນຄ້າຈາກບໍລິສັດອື່ນອອກ (%(bad_products)s)."

